Books for Penetration Testers, Programmers and Bug Hunters

1. Breaking into Information Security (Gill)
  getting started in an information security carrer with an emphasis on offensive security

2.linux basics for hackers (OccupyTheWeb)
  reads like atutorial with practical tips and application

3.Pentration Testing: A Hands-On Introduction to Hacking
  core skills and techniques every pentester needs.

4.The Basics of Hacking and Penetration Testing:
  Ethical Hacking and Penetration Testing Made Easy

5. CEH v10 Certified Ethical Hacker Study Guide 1st Edition
   chapters are organised by exam objective
